	display.
	(w3m-goto-url): Ditto.
	(w3m-exec-process): Use `sleep-for' instead of `sit-for'.
	(w3m-toggle-inline-images): Set cursor point before image insertion.
	(w3m-goto-url): Set cursor point before redisplay.

